#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:5 288f1332139d4555b2d1be3528d293dd
msgid "User Buffer Registration"
msgstr "用户缓冲区注册"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:7 5b34b2d20bdf44b4bc3e3aff83680b74
msgid ""
"User Buffer Registration is a feature that allows NCCL to directly send/receive/operate data through the user buffer "
"without extra internal copy. It can accelerate collectives and reduce the resource usage (e.g. #channel usage)."
msgstr "用户缓冲区注册功能允许NCCL直接通过用户缓冲区执行发送/接收/操作数据，无需额外的内部拷贝。该功能可加速集合通信操作并降低资源消耗（例如减少信道使用量）。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:10 666238112fff431b90921e2b7f61c434
msgid ""
"NCCL 2.19.x now supports user buffer registration for NVLink Switch; any NCCL collectives that support NVLS algorithm "
"can utilize this feature. To enable the *CUDA Graph based* buffer registration, users have to comply with several "
"requirements:"
msgstr "NCCL 2.19.x 现已支持面向NVLink交换机的用户缓冲区注册；任何支持NVLS算法的NCCL集合通信操作均可利用此功能。要启用*基于CUDA图*的缓冲区注册，用户需满足以下要求："

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:13 ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:21
#: 8b178523707b44e2afc42a20c5297cfd eedcbe1c016845a8841b942da0d89171
msgid "The buffer is allocated through :c:func:`ncclMemAlloc()`."
msgstr "缓冲区通过 :c:func:`ncclMemAlloc()` 进行分配。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:14 f5b0efb904454e2788656a97849d8fd9
msgid "Offset to the head address of the buffer is same for each rank in collectives."
msgstr "集合通信操作中，每个秩的缓冲区首地址偏移量保持相同。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:15 1bc0ed7722a344cfb49091b177f412d2
msgid "The NCCL operation is launched on a stream captured by a CUDA graph."
msgstr "NCCL操作在由CUDA图捕获的流上启动。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:17 f5df82a806f444bea651f97a73e8b9cf
msgid "Registered buffers will be deregistered when cuda graph is destroyed."
msgstr "已注册的缓冲区将在CUDA图销毁时自动解除注册。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:19 b918cd85c10e46018081029ef4fd36a7
msgid ""
"On the other hand, to enable the *Local based* buffer registration, users have to comply with the following "
"requirements:"
msgstr "另一方面，要启用*基于本地*的缓冲区注册，用户必须满足以下要求："

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:22 6cd1c93f278745b082e73f425ed3c795
msgid "Register buffer with :c:func:`ncclCommRegister` before calling collectives."
msgstr "在调用集合通信操作前，使用 :c:func:`ncclCommRegister` 注册缓冲区。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:23 f02b0a419fbb46c1b3fdd8c3f22e73dd
msgid "Call NCCL collectives as usual but similarly keep the offset to the head address of the buffer same for each rank."
msgstr "照常调用NCCL集合通信操作，但同样保持每个秩的缓冲区首地址偏移量一致。"

#: ../../source/usage/bufferreg.rst:25 491181c2038e423a97ba125f72ea6510
msgid "Registered buffers will be deregistered when users explicitly call :c:func:`ncclCommDeregister`."
msgstr "已注册的缓冲区将在用户显式调用 :c:func:`ncclCommDeregister` 时解除注册。"
